Package org.apache.jackrabbit.webdav.lock

Class SupportedLock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jackrabbit.webdav.property.AbstractDavProperty<java.util.List<LockEntry>>
      • org.apache.jackrabbit.webdav.lock.SupportedLock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DavConstants, DavProperty<java.util.List<LockEntry>>, PropEntry, XmlSerializable
    public class SupportedLock
extends AbstractDavProperty<java.util.List<LockEntry>>
    The SupportedLock class encapsulates the lock capabilities of a resource. It is mainly responsible for generating the <supportedlock> property.
